DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to retrospectively review the impact of vaginal packing on the urodynamic studies, especially for urethral pressure profiles.
DOC.brief_title: Changes of Pad Weight Results and Urethral Pressure Profiles After Reduction of Cystocele by Vaginal Gauze Packing
DOC.criteria: patients with >= stage II cystocele and underwent urodynamic studies patients less than 20 patients
